-03-29 |url-status=bot: unknown |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20041010162606/http://www.adn.com/front/story/5572779p-5504444c.html |archivedate=October 10, 2004 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"THR_Hibberd_20101115\">{{cite news|title='Sarah Palin's Alaska' Breaks TLC Ratings Record |first=James |last=Hibberd |work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=November 15, 2010 |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/blogs/live-feed/sarah-palins-alaska-breaks-tlc-45421 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110805114926/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/blogs/live-feed/sarah-palins-alaska-breaks-tlc-45421 |archivedate=August 5, 2011 |accessdate=August 18, 2011 |url-status=dead |df=mdy }}</ref>\n\n}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Sister project links|wikt=no|v=no|s=no|b=no|species=no|d=Q43144}}\n{{Wiktionary|Palinista|Palinism|refudiate}}\n* [http://www.sarahpac.com/ SarahPAC (Sarah Palin Political Action Committee)]\n* {{YouTube|u=SarahPalinAK|{{PAGENAMEBASE}}}}\n* {{IMDb name|3126606}}\n* {{curlie|Regional/North_America/United_States/Society_and_Culture/Politics/Parties/Republican/People/Palin,_Sarah}}\n* {{C-SPAN|Sarah Palin}}\n\n{{Navboxes\n|title=Sarah Palin succession and navigation boxes\n|state=collapsed\n|list1=\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-off}}\n{{s-bef|before=John Stein}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Mayor of [[Wasilla, Alaska|Wasilla]]|years=1996\u20132002}}\n{{s-aft|after=Dianne Keller}}\n\n{{s-bef|before=[[Frank Murkowski]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[List of Governors of Alaska|Governor of Alaska]]|years=2006\u20132009}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Sean Parnell]]}}\n\n{{s-ppo}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Frank Murkowski]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]] nominee for [[List of Governors of Alaska|Governor of Alaska]]|years=[[Alaska gubernatorial election, 2006|2006]]}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Sean Parnell]]}}\n\n{{s-bef|before=[[Dick Cheney]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]] [[List of United States Republican Party presidential tickets|nominee]] for [[Vi